ActEeyou Marine Region Land Claims Agreement Act
SubjectAmendments to the Eeyou Marine Region Land Claims Agreement (Article 5.8.7)
PrecisOrder amending the EEYOU MARINE REGION LAND CLAIMS AGREEMENT in order to reflect the fulfilment of the obligations contained in article 5.8.7 of the agreement regarding the completion of contaminant remediation of Bear Island and the land exchange of Bear Island and Grey Goose Island as Cree Lands for a parcel of South Twin Island as Federal Crown Land.
